NG0762:96: bsnyen sngags sgrub sngags las sbyor gsum //

NG0762:426: rag sha srin po sa mu dza //
NG0762:427: rag sha ru tra hum b+h+yo /
NG0762:428: ru gnyen nag po cho cho sa //

NG0762:430: gtor ha ba le hob la thun b+h+yo /

NG0762:82: nya stong brgyad gsum gtor ma gtang *//
NG0762:112: rin chen 'bar ba'i gzugs su bya //

NG0762:438: pa'o // // de nas yang gsang ba'i bdag pos

NG0762:447: gsang ba srog rgyud ces kyang grags //
NG0762:448: dregs pa spyi yi rgyud 'dus pas //
NG0762:449: dregs pa spyi rgyud ces kyang bya //

NG0762:451: gtso mchog chen po'i rgyud ces bya //
NG0762:452: sems can kun gyi mgon mdzad pas //
NG0762:453: mgon po'i rgyud chen zhes kyang bya //
NG0762:454: pho mo klu gsum 'dir dril bas //
NG0762:455: dril rgyud chen po zhes kyang bya //
NG0762:456: dgra bgegs thams cad 'dir sgrol bas //
NG0762:457: drag po sgrol rgyud ces kyang bya //
NG0762:458: pho mo gang du ma nges shing *//
NG0762:459: sangs rgyas 'phrin las bdag mdzad pas //

NG0762:462: 'di ni nor bu rin po che //

NG0762:464: rgyud 'di rin chen gser gyis bris //
NG0762:465: rtag tu mi 'bral lus la bcang *//
NG0762:466: phyi nang gsang ba'i rten rdzas bcang *//
NG0762:467: rgyun du bsnyen sgrub nar mar byed //
NG0762:468: dus kyi mchod pa mi bcag cing *//

NG0762:470: chos skyong ma ning gtso 'khor la //
NG0762:471: brtse gdung gus pa rgyun mi bcad //
NG0762:472: dpal mgon ma ning las rgyud 'di //
NG0762:474: dbul ba mi nus stong zhus byed //
NG0762:475: dad gus med cing g.yo khram byed //
NG0762:476: rab 'bring tha ma'i zhabs tog med //
NG0762:477: pha ma dkon mchog mi 'khur zhing *//
NG0762:478: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i spyi tshogs @#//
NG0762:481: kha gsag stong zhus nyams len mi skyong dang *//
NG0762:482: gnag pa snying rus med cing blo mi brtan //
NG0762:483: de lta bu la bka' 'di gsang *//
NG0762:484: dad med g.yem la phyar la bka' 'di gsang *//
NG0762:485: dam tshig sdom pa nyams la bka' 'di gsang *//
NG0762:486: snod med rang dgar mod la bka' 'di gsang *//
NG0762:487: skal med rang don can la bka' 'di gsang *//
NG0762:488: de lta bu la 'di shor na //
NG0762:489: rgyal khams mes sregs bskal pa chus 'khru bas //
NG0762:490: de bas rab tu nan tan gces //
NG0762:491: mgo la me 'bar khong du sbrul zhugs kyang *//
NG0762:492: chu srin gre bar rin chen tshud pa bzhin //
NG0762:493: bskal pa 'khrug kyang khar mi dbyung *//
NG0762:494: gong bstan snod med rnams la 'di spel na //
NG0762:495: ma ning nag po nyid kyis srog rtsa chad //
NG0762:496: srog thig nag pos tshe yi 'du byed bskul //
NG0762:497: lha srin sde brgyad rnams kyis bka' 'di srungs //
NG0762:498: nam zhig las can rdo rje thod 'phreng rtsal //
NG0762:499: spyan ras gzigs sprul 'di la bka' 'di gtod //
NG0762:500: des kyang gter nas gter du sbos //
NG0762:501: da ki las kyi dbang mo che //
NG0762:502: mkha' 'gro gtso mo khyod kyis bka' 'di srungs //
NG0762:503: ched du gnyer ro shor ra re //
NG0762:504: nam zhig dus kyi tha ma la //
NG0762:505: sems can rnams ni nyon mongs rang dgar spyod //
NG0762:506: chos pa rnams ni chos gzhung spangs nas chos brgyad skyong *//
NG0762:507: sgom chen sgom sgrub mi byed bsod nams skyong *//
NG0762:508: gsang sngags bskyed rdzogs chos rnams skyangs la //
NG0762:509: dge bshes thos bsam spangs nas bzang rdzus byed //
NG0762:510: mtshan nyid sde gsum chos la yang *//
NG0762:511: dge bcu pha rol phyin drug dang *//
NG0762:512: lam lnga sa bcu spyod mkhan med //
NG0762:513: dkon mchog gsum gyi dbu 'phang dma' //
NG0762:514: dus gsum sangs rgyas bstan pa nyams //
NG0762:515: gtsug lag khang la bdag 'dzin phyugs ra byed //
NG0762:516: de'i tshe sems can thams cad kun //
NG0762:517: bdag 'dzin ru tra khengs pa'i tshe //
NG0762:518: de dus skal ldan byang sems can //
NG0762:519: sngon dus sa lam rab sbyangs ba //
NG0762:520: de dus kun la snying rje che //
NG0762:521: rgyu 'bras chos kun ma lus mkhyen //
NG0762:522: rig pa'i gnas kun blo kha bye //
NG0762:523: rigs rtsal phyogs med kun sgrol bdag / blo brtan blo zab blo che ba //
NG0762:524: gsang sngags spyi gnad kun la goms //
NG0762:525: bla ma la gus gtong phod che //
NG0762:526: dbang rigs yongs rdzogs mched la dung *//
NG0762:527: gtsug lag khang skyong stan tshis che //
NG0762:528: rang don ma yin gzhan don brtson //
NG0762:529: lus srog bab kyang chos mi 'dor //
NG0762:530: bla ma'i bka' tsam mi cog cing *//
NG0762:531: yi dam bsnyen sgrub mi cog pa //
NG0762:532: chos skyong dus mchod mi cog pa //
NG0762:533: gtsang rme chung zhing dpa' brtul che //
NG0762:534: de lta bu yi skal ldan la //
NG0762:535: bka' 'di ston cig sa ma ya //
NG0762:536: des kyang rang don ma yin gzhan don du //
NG0762:537: bdag 'dzin ru tra thams cad bsgral //
NG0762:539: dpal mgon ma ning gsang ba 'phrin las nag po'i rgyud chen po las / @#//
NG0762:540: mtshan gyis rnam grangs bstan pa dang */
NG0762:541: snod med la gsang zhing snod ldan la gtad pa'i le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o ///
NG0762:542: / de nas yum khro mo gnam zhal ma dang */
NG0762:543: rigs 'dzin chen po rdo rje chos dang */
NG0762:544: gsang ba'i bdag po lag na rdo rje mgrin gcig tu bstod pa /
NG0762:545: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NG0762:546: chos sku skye med ngang nas ni //
NG0762:547: longs sku 'gag med dpal chen sku //
NG0762:549: ru tra bdud sde dpung bcas ma lus thul //
NG0762:550: rtsal chen thogs med khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0762:551: dpal chen sku gsung thugs las sprul pa'i sku //
NG0762:552: ma rungs 'dul dka' bdud sde ji snyed btul //
NG0762:553: lha yul sum cu rtsa gsum gnas su lha yi dmag dpon mdzad //
NG0762:554: phrag dog lha ma yin rnams brlag par mdzad //
NG0762:555: lha rnams g.yul rgyal bstan par dar rgyas mdzad //
NG0762:556: lha chen dpal 'bar khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0762:557: lha dbang brgya byin dang lha'i bu mo bye ba phrag mang pos bstod pa /
NG0762:558: ma la ya yi rtse mo ru //
NG0762:559: dur khrod thod mkhar me rlung tshub dkyil du //
NG0762:560: ru tra sde gsum sde brgyad ma lus btul //
NG0762:561: gsang sngags bskyed rdzogs bstan pa dar rgyas mdzad //
NG0762:562: dpal mgon ma ning sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0762:563: mi thod pa can gyis bstod pa /
NG0762:564: bsil ba tshal gyi dur khrod du //
NG0762:565: lta log sum brgya drug cu bcom //
NG0762:566: grub mtha' ngan pa kun tshar bcad //
NG0762:567: mu stegs bstan pa gtan nas brlag / zhing skyong ma mo mkha' 'gros bskor //
NG0762:568: nag po chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0762:569: srid rtsa bdag 'dzin 'dul la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0762:570: pha rol phyin drug spyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0762:571: spyod pa rlabs chen 'phags la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0762:572: srid rtsa bdag 'dzin gzi mdangs can la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0762:573: rtsal chen gzi mdangs can la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0762:574: nag po thod 'phreng khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0762:575: rigs 'dzin srog shing khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0762:576: sa chu mnga' bdag khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0762:577: bdud 'dul dbang phyug khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0762:578: tshogs kyi bdag po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0762:579: gtsug lag khang skyong khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0762:580: ces don dang mthun pas bstod do //
NG0762:581: de nas yum khro mo gnam zhal ma dang */
NG0762:582: sprul pa'i mgon po rnams dang */
NG0762:583: ma ning mched bzhi la sogs pa rnams 'od du gyur nas /
NG0762:585: dpa' bo yab chen che mchog he ru ka snang la rang bzhin med pa /
NG0762:586: nam mkha'i 'ja' tshon ltar dbyings su thim mo //
NG0762:587: slar yang sprul pa du ma 'gyed do //
NG0762:588: de nas rigs 'dzin gsang ba'i bdag po dang */
NG0762:589: lha ma srin sde brgyad dang */
NG0762:590: ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro las kyi dbang mo che dang */
NG0762:591: 'khor mkha' 'gro bye ba 'bum phrag du ma dang */
NG0762:596: lang+ka dur khrod bdag po dang */
NG0762:597: bdud 'dul nyi khri chig stong gi tshogs dang */
NG0762:599: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
NG0762:600: dpal chen po sku gsung thugs kyi sprul pa ye

NG0762:602: sangs rgyas kyi 'phrin las mdzad pa'i ma ning las
